                                <h4 class="panel-title"> <a class="collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent=".accordion" href="#collapse-curriculum-16" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse-curriculum-16"> <span class="left">6</span> <span class="right">Hadoop Ecosystems</span> </a> </h4>
