                                        <li>Run MapReduce programs</li>
                                        <li>Run HIVE scripts/jobs.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p><strong>Hands on:</strong></p>
                                    <p>Create the Workflow to incremental Imports of Sqoop. Create the Workflow for Pig, Hive and Sqoop Exports. And also execute Coordinator to Schedule the Workflows.</p>
                                    <p><strong><br>6.6 FLUME</strong></p>
                                    <p><strong>Learning Objectives:</strong></p>
                                    <p>Understand Flume Architecture and its components Source, Channel and Sinks. Configure flume with Socket, File Sources and HDFS and Hbase Sink. Understand Fan In and Fan Out Architecture.</p>
