                                    <div class="panel-body">
                                        <div class="editor-content">
                                            <p>By the end of this course, you will learn about Big Data and Big Data Challenges. You will also gain knowledge of the Hadoop Daemon Processes, HDFS, Hadoop Installation Modes, and HDFS, Hadoop Developer Tasks, Hadoop Ecosystems, Data Analytics using Pentaho as an ETL tool.</p>
